00:12:21.450 --> 00:12:24.390
So there are clearly
problems, right?

00:12:24.390 --> 00:12:27.090
And it seemed to me, when I was
given the challenge of opening

00:12:27.090 --> 00:12:28.830
up this magnificent
lecture series you're

00:12:28.830 --> 00:12:30.494
having, that if I
was going to talk

00:12:30.494 --> 00:12:32.910
about the causes of health,
like, I felt like you couldn't

00:12:32.910 --> 00:12:34.868
start this lecture series
without understanding

00:12:34.868 --> 00:12:36.030
these basic facts.

00:12:36.030 --> 00:12:37.180
Now this is the US.

00:12:37.180 --> 00:12:39.000
I just want to,
just for a second,

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:42.260
make a quick global comment,
because ultimately this

00:12:42.260 --> 00:12:43.620
has to be a global lens.

00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:47.470
So let me just go back to a
