00:47:16.255 --> 00:47:18.046
it's very busy,
particularly combining that

00:47:18.046 --> 00:47:19.310
with one's own scholarship.

00:47:19.310 --> 00:47:22.870
So I don't have much time for a
pet, but I do have a goldfish.

00:47:22.870 --> 00:47:24.750
And I love my goldfish.

00:47:24.750 --> 00:47:28.220
And I want my goldfish
to be healthy.

00:47:28.220 --> 00:47:31.220
So I say to my
goldfish, we're going

00:47:31.220 --> 00:47:34.720
to genotype you to figure out
