00:47:34.720 --> 00:47:36.470
so that when you are
sick, we can give you

00:47:36.470 --> 00:47:39.170
the perfect
personalized medicine

00:47:39.170 --> 00:47:42.860
for your particular
little fishy disease.

00:47:42.860 --> 00:47:45.332
I say to my goldfish,
you need to exercise.

00:47:45.332 --> 00:47:47.040
So I want you to swim
10 times clockwise,

00:47:47.040 --> 00:47:49.090
10 times counterclockwise in
your little bowl every day.

00:47:49.090 --> 00:47:51.290
And when I feed you little
flaky food, don't eat too much,

00:47:51.290 --> 00:47:51.890
don't get fat.

00:47:51.890 --> 00:47:53.580
And when you have a
goldfish companion,

00:47:53.580 --> 00:47:55.121
make sure you have
safe goldfish sex.

00:47:55.121 --> 00:47:57.506
I say all these
things to my goldfish.

00:47:57.506 --> 00:47:58.630
And I'm like, OK, I got it.

00:47:58.630 --> 00:47:59.534
I nailed this.

00:47:59.534 --> 00:48:01.200
And one day, I walk
